          <div class="faq-answer">True autopilot (publish without weekly input) costs $49–$199/month. theStacc at $99/month is the strongest value — 30 articles, GBP automation, review responses, and social publishing in one subscription. Budget content-only tools like Journalist AI and Byword start at $29–$49/month but require more manual configuration.</div>
